Paper Submission:
-----------------

Papers must be submitted electronically via the CORCS 2009 Submission 
Page. The format of submitted papers should follow the guidelines for 
the IEEE conference proceedings. All papers will be carefully reviewed 
by at least three reviewers. Papers should be no more than 6 pages.


